Depends: python3, python3-yaml, {{ DEPS }}
Recommends: podman, buildah
Description: convert a docker-compose stack into a single bootc LXC OCI image
 Host-callable, daemonless converter that transposes a docker-compose stack into
 a self-contained bootc image whose services run under Podman + Quadlet (no
 Docker daemon, no Docker socket), following the same atomic/ostree model as the
 DaemonCores-VE images. The produced image is what pvect-ostree deploys as an
 immutable, unprivileged Proxmox container.
 .
 Every service becomes a Quadlet .container sharing one Quadlet .network, so
 services still resolve each other by their compose service name. Persistent data
 is relocated under /var/lib/compose2bootc (the only mutable location a bootc
 image ships). Ships a 7-day healthcheck-gated rebuild timer per stack.
